This repository contains the codes and data generated throughout the project.

Codes are separated into different categories depending on their function, and labelled based on running order where appropiate.

The data is also divided into the main sections discussed in the report. Unless otherwise specified, the cross-sections use the same Gaussian and smoothing parameters as described in the text: Gauss width 2 and 6 for stacks including pS, Gaussian width 2 for only-multiples stacks of the whole crust, and Gaussian width 6 for stacks of the shallow crust.

The raw data of receiver functions migrated to depth was too big to include in the GitHub, but can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a5our8_1i8jDgZZchqIlyE-Wq4lBXuFs